    strong
      | *
    |  Open sidebar 
  = off.content do |c|
    = c.header do
      = c.title { 'Sidebar content' }
      = c.close_button class: 'btn btn-info' do
        |  Close 
    = c.body do
      p
        | Some content in the sidebar!



